    "field_description": "\nOur current space infrastructure is constrained by legacy models and high costs. By leveraging commercial approaches, innovative construction methods, and new research in planetary engineering and interstellar exploration, we can break free from these limitations and open the door to a new era of space development. Some of these projects are larger than “bridge scale”.\n\n",
